    "en": {
      "title": "Recapture of a diesel-laden vehicle by the public in Sammanthurai",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "In Sammanthurai, 18 cans of diesel were seized in a suspicious step vehicle by the public.",
        "The public has reported that this has happened several times on several occasions through one of these diesel and petrol stations.",
        "In this situation, yesterday (27) at 12.30 am in the Sammanthurai clock tower area, the public who were waiting for fuel said that they noticed the vehicle.",
        "A scuffle ensued between the driver and the driver of the vehicle, who were aware that about 18 containers of diesel had been filled when the vehicle was returned to the vehicle on suspicion and the public was waiting for refueling under the Sammanthurai clock tower.",
        "After the public informed the police, the officer in charge of the Sammanthurai police station and the police seized the vehicle and after confirming the presence of diesel in the cans, the vehicle was taken to the Sammanthurai police station."
      ],
